        "body": "<pre><code>pets[1].count = 50;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>This will raise <code>java.lang.NullPointerException<\/code> as <code>pets[1]<\/code> reference is <code>null<\/code>. <\/p>\n\n<pre><code>System.out.println(pets[0].count);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>If you commented out the previous line, then this will definitely print 43.<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>System.out.println(pets[1].count);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>If commented out <code>pets[1].count = 50;<\/code> line, then it would raise same <code>java.lang.NullPointerException<\/code> as <code>pets[1]<\/code> reference is <code>null<\/code>.<\/p>\n\n<p>In short you forgot to initialise <code>pets[1]<\/code> which should be -<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>pets[1] = new Echo();\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
